{
  "stem": "24346.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had German engineers drilling holes, putting in dynamite, ripping out, and when a rock got loose, we lay tracks, and we had to pick it up by hand, fill up the tracks, take it out, and so they can go further.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In other words, we started building another factory like the one existed in Dora.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I had what I said, this clothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not warmer clothing, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we had to get up in the morning, every morning, to go to this work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got so used to this work, because I had one of the people who took care of the barrack-- he was a German from Vienna, happened to be a very young man.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know why he picked me, but he beated me every day for no reason at all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He started beating me with a, with a rubber-- it was covered with rubber, something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, after the war, when I complained to the Germans, I said, this [NON-ENGLISH], this guy hit me over the head constantly.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they took me for x-rays.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I complained on that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I told them what happened in that camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He just picked on me, I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was, it came to a point where I told the kapo-- it was a Polish guy, what he worked-- I was young, work didn't mean a thing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Even though I didn't have enough food, I worked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because I didn't want to get beatings for saying, hey, you're standing around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I worked and I didn't get beaten.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When we came to march home, I told this-- it was a Polish kapo, and he was a little sympathetic, this guy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I said, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Ludzig, ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Ludzig-- ?] well, I remember his name, so many years-- [?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
